      "message": "[Critical] Line 247: 🔴 Critical Issues - The scoped services `clearSwarmBodyOverwriteConversation` and `bodyOverwriteLoadedConversation` ignore the `DLPlugin*` argument and trust the caller-provided account/conversation pair. That lets any plugin clear or trigger body-overwrite processing for conversations where it is not enabled. Apply the same authorization check used by `updateMessageBodyOverwrite` before touching the conversation.\n\n```suggestion\nauto clearSwarmBodyOverwriteConversation \u003d [this](const DLPlugin* plugin, void* data) {\n    const auto* p \u003d static_cast\u003cstd::pair\u003cstd::string, std::string\u003e*\u003e(data);\n    if (!p)\n        return -1;\n    if (!getEnabledConversationsForPlugin(plugin).contains(*p))\n        return -1;\n    // existing lookup and clearBodyOverwrites()\n    return 0;\n};\n```",
